You need to add a new section `queries` under you app&#39;s `&lt;manifest&gt;` tag with desired package name:

    &lt;manifest package=&quot;com.example.app&quot;&gt;
        &lt;queries&gt;
            &lt;package android:name=&quot;com.whatsapp&quot; /&gt;
        &lt;/queries&gt;
      ...
    &lt;/manifest&gt;

